<template>
  <button @click="logout">Logout</button>
</template>
<script>
import axios from 'axios';
// import axios from "axios";
export default {
  methods: {
    // async CreatePost() {
    //   let response = await axios.post("logout");
    // },
    logout() {
      localStorage.removeItem("token");
      this.$router.push("/apiLogin");
    },
    async logout() {
      const response=await axios.post("/logout").then(localStorage.removeItem("token")).catch((error))
    },
  },
};
</script>
